 offers an\ninteresting way to cope with swimmers on the basis of ordinary differential\nequations, allowing for analytical tractability and efficient numerical\ntreatment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Dec 2021 16:48:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
