 number of\nnew results on both sides. One such example is a new Cauchy identity which\nnaturally pairs our superconformal blocks with Sergeev-Veselov super Jacobi\npolynomials and yields the CPW decomposition of any free theory diagram in any\ndimension.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Dec 2021 19:03:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2022 19:35:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-16"}
