LR=-1%). Conclusion. We unveil many interactions between said\nhuman factors and bias. Additionally, we use prediction models to confirm and\nreveal even more interactions. Significance. This paper is a first step towards\nidentifying optimal biased feedback for a personality type, state, and CP in\norder to maximize BCI performance and learning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Dec 2021 07:51:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-24"}
