 quantify and predict aging\nof lithium-ion batteries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Dec 2021 09:15:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2022 06:58:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-01"}
